4. CONTENT CREATION & MONETIZATION
──────────────────────────────────

Trafkhop Entertainment™ encourages the creation of videos and images
featuring our projects. You may share and monetize your content on
video-sharing and social media platforms (such as YouTube, Twitch, etc.)
subject to the following rules:

* Monetization is permitted ONLY through official platform-provided
  monetization methods (e.g., YouTube Partner Program, Twitch Affiliates).
* You are encouraged to provide your own creative input (commentary,
  reviews, or transformative editing).
* Simple copies of gameplay or music without any original contribution
  are NOT permitted, unless using official system sharing functions.
* You may only use content that has been officially released to the
  public or from official promotional material (trailers, etc.).
* You must not state or imply that your content is official, sponsored,
  or endorsed by Trafkhop Entertainment™.
* We reserve the right to remove or object to any content we deem
  unlawful, inappropriate, or non-compliant with these guidelines.

